info.name: Chicken Tikka Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | Chicken marinated with a blend of spices and grilled till succulent & tender is filled in a freshly rolled out warm paratha along with crisp veggies to make this delicious street food snack.

info.name: Batata Vada Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | The iconic Mumbai street food gets a healthy twist! This unique & delicious roll is packed with soft Batata Vada and fresh veggies. A hint of mint sauce & this roll will take you back in time! (490 Calories)

info.name: Bhuna Chicken Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | Chicken tossed in a spicy mix & cooked in its own juices until it is perfectly dry yet full of flavour. This delicous chicken is tied together in a freshly rolled out paratha with our in house sauce. (440 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Shami Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | The amazing Shami Kebabs now inside a paratha! These soft kebabs are a blend of chicken mince & lentils cooked to perfection. The crisp soft kebabs are wrapped in a delicious paratha with mint sauce. (530 Calories)

info.name: Chilli Paneer Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | Just the right flavour of spicy chilli paneer - a juicy Kaati roll with freshly chopped veggies & soft paneer tossed & cooked in the right spices. (440 Calories)

info.name: Egg and Cheese Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | When soulmates Egg & Cheese come together inside a roll, it?s a match made in heaven! Combined with freshly chopped greens and a delicious sauce, this classic Kaati roll is perfect for a dinner! (500 Calories)

info.name: Mixed Veg Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | A light roll high on the goodness of veggies. Assorted vegetables, sourced locally are spiced & rolled into the paratha along with our delicious mint sauce. This is health in a paratha! (420 Calories)

info.name: Paneer Tikka Roll
info.description: Serves 1 | A delicious and satisfying meal by itself that can be enjoyed as a quick lunch or snack. Perfectly marinated and grilled paneer is wrapped in a paratha along with fresh veggies and served with chutney

info.name: Schezwan Chicken Roll
